

## Load Balancers in AWS

--> Accepts incoming trafiis from client
--> Routes requests to its EC2 instances in one or more zones
--> Application Load Balancers
--> Network Load Balancers
--> Classic Load Balancers
 
--> Improves application availabiliy and responsiveness
--> Prevent server overload

